                    <span>I saw this on World Link TV one night when nothing else was on. I was completely captivated, enchanted, blown away. Words cannot describe this film or the way it shifted/stretched my consciousness. I felt like a child being playfully tossed into the air of a greater understanding of (and trust in) how the entire intelligent universe unfolds itself. A complete joy! I've got to find this on DVD....</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">"Survivor" at the cellular level</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
